    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Artists who specialize in paintings on animal hide, usually American bison or elk; term is usually used for First Nations or Native American artists, including those of the traditional Plains Indian artistic tradition.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
